---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — Return App" description="Terms of Service for the Return mobile application." lang="en">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 pt-32 pb-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 leading-tight mb-2">Terms of Service.</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-light mb-10">Last Updated: June 30, 2026</p>

    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      Welcome to <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Return</strong> (the "App"), a freemium breathing and mood-tracking mobile application. These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your use of the App and our website hosted at returnapp.org (the "Service"). 
    </p>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      The Service is operated by a private individual based in Zürich, Switzerland ("we", "us", or "our"). By accessing or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the App.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">1. Eligibility & Age Restrictions</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      By using Return, you represent and warrant that you are at least <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">13 years of age</strong>. The Service is not intended for, nor directed at, children under the age of 13. If you are under 13, you are strictly prohibited from using the App.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">2. Medical Disclaimer</h2>
    <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-500/50 pl-4 text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10 italic">
      <strong class="text-amber-400 font-medium not-italic block mb-2">⚠️ IMPORTANT HEALTH NOTICE:</strong>
      Return is a tool designed to assist with personal wellness, breathing exercises, and general mood tracking. <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Return does not provide medical, psychological, or psychiatric advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</strong> The App is not a medical device. If you experience severe anxiety, shortness of breath, or any health issues, please consult a qualified healthcare professional immediately. Never disregard professional medical advice because of something you experienced through the App.
    </div>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">3. Local Data Storage & User Responsibility</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Your privacy is built into our architecture. All breathing sessions, mood tracking logs, and personal metrics entered into the App are <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">stored exclusively on your local device</strong>.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10 pl-2">
      <li><strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Data Control:</strong> You have full control over your data. You can delete all your data directly within the App or export it at any time into a .csv file.</li>
      <li><strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Risk of Data Loss:</strong> Because we do not store your data on external servers, <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">we cannot recover your data if it is lost.</strong> If you delete the App, lose your device, or clear your device cache without exporting your data, your logs will be permanently deleted.</li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">4. Freemium Model & In-App Purchases (IAP)</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Return is offered on a freemium basis. Basic features are free, while premium features require in-app purchases or subscriptions.
    </p>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      All financial transactions, billing, and subscriptions are processed and managed exclusively through the <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Apple App Store</strong> (for iOS devices) and the <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">Google Play Store</strong> (for Android devices). Your purchases are subject to the terms, conditions, and refund policies of Apple Inc. or Google LLC, respectively. We do not collect, store, or process any payment or credit card details.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      All rights, title, and interest in and to the App (excluding user-generated local data), including its code, design, interface, branding, and logos, are the exclusive property of the developer. You are granted a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use the App for personal, non-commercial purposes.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      To the maximum extent permitted by Swiss law, the developer shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including but not limited to loss of data, personal injury, emotional distress, or device failure arising out of your use of or inability to use the App. The App is provided on an "AS IS" and "AS AVAILABLE" basis.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">7. Governing Law and Jurisdiction</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
      These Terms and your use of the App shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">substantive laws of Switzerland</strong>, excluding its conflict of law provisions. Any disputes arising out of or in connection with these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the <strong class="text-slate-100 font-medium">courts of Zürich, Switzerland</strong>.
    </p>

    <hr class="border-slate-800 my-10" />

    <h2 class="text-xl font-light tracking-tight text-slate-50 mb-4">8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed mb-10">
       Please reach out to us at: 
       <a href="mailto:info@returnapp.org" class="text-sapphire-400 hover:text-sapphire-300 transition-colors">info@returnapp.org</a>
    </p>
